1. Add xft into USE.

2. Install:
  emerge xfce4-screensaver xfce4-power-manager rxvt-unicode feh liberation-fonts dejavu alsa-utils dmenu xdotool scrot urxvt-perls

3. Copy files:
  .xinitrc -> ~/.xinitrc
  .Xresources -> ~/.Xresources
  xmonad.hs.example -> xmonad.hs
  xmobar.hs.example -> xmobar.hs
  pasta -> /usr/lib64/urxvt/perl/pasta

4. Change xmonad.hs and xmobar.hs

5. Compile:
  xmonad --recompile && xmonad --restart
